</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'>pandoc code.txt -s --highlight-style pygments<span class="o">[</span>tango|kate|..<span class="o">]</span> -o example.html
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


